1. cs.RO (Robotics) - The paper focuses on object segmentation in robotics applications, specifically for grasped objects. 
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper uses deep learning for object detection and segmentation, which is a core topic in computer vision. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper leverages self-recognition networks for object segmentation, which falls under the umbrella of AI. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses machine learning techniques for object segmentation, specifically deep learning and self-recognition networks. 
5. cs.ROBOTS (Robots and Robot Systems) - The paper's focus on object segmentation in robotics applications makes it likely to be categorized under this sub-category.
